<br>
Maladominus was among the early batch of LoS members that Gray recruited early in his leadership of the Shadows. <br>
<br>
those were the early days when I remember Gray appointed both Morgrist and Antoin as the quartermasters to take charge of League possessions and the armory.  and the early raids into Castle Mistmoore and soon after we started to hit ToFS...<br>
<br>
Gray and his womens.... well yes, the Maladominus has mysteriously forgotten about that part of history, yes yes. <br>
<br>
Oh and there was the time when Our Great Leader Gray was once clean-shaven.... and then he decided to sport a beard, and then The Didi always teased Gray mercilessly about that.... <br>
